did.abstract: This collection consists of the publications of the Academy of Management in paper form. For publications in digital form see collection 5289 PUBS(d). The Kheel Center continues to receive all current AoM publications, which are added to this collection.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: In March 2019 the container list for this collection was rearranged by Academy of Management Divison and thereunder publication title, then date.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the collections in the Kheel Center is restricted. Please contact a reference archivist for access to these materials.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: This collection must be used in keeping with the Kheel Center Information Sheet and Procedures for Document Use.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: AoM Publications #5289 PUBS. Kheel Center for Labor-Management Documentation and Archives, Cornell University Library.
